properties.name: Robert Good
properties.biography: Good received a bachelor's degree in finance and a master's degree in leadership from Liberty University. He worked at CitiFinancial as a branch manager, area training director, and district manager from 1988 to 2005, after which he began working as a senior associate athletic director for development and executive director of the Flames Club at Liberty University.
